down.</p>
<p><sup><a name="fn91" href="#fnB91">[87]</a></sup> 	There were seven cases
where the existence of family violence was noted in the judgment without any
further discussion of it, and
there were several other cases in which the
description of the marriage suggested indicia of abuse.</p>
<p><sup><a name="fn92" href="#fnB92">[88]</a></sup> 	Grania Sheehan and Bruce
